com.aylanetworks.aylasdk

类 AylaPropertyTrigger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.AylaPropertyTrigger

  • public class AylaPropertyTrigger
extends java.lang.Object
    Property triggers are used to launch an action when a specified condition is met on the device. This object is used by createTrigger,updateTrigger,fetchTriggers and deleteTrigger methods in AylaProperty object

        public AylaAPIRequest deleteApp(AylaPropertyTriggerApp triggerApp,

                                ErrorListener errorListener)
        Deletes a Trigger App
        参数:
        triggerApp - AylaPropertyTriggerApp that needs to be deleted. This is the existing TriggerApp that has been fetched from service
